# Bryan Dashboard - Environment Variables
#
# This is a WASM frontend app. Most settings (RPC URLs, Etherscan API key)
# are configured through the in-app Settings pane and stored in localStorage.
#
# No environment variables are required to run the app.
# The variables below are optional and only used during development/build.

# Dioxus CLI dev server port (default: 8080)
# DIOXUS_PORT=8080
